      "qolie89_bother3": "Somewhat",
      "qolie89_bother4": "Quite a bit",
      "qolie89_bother5": "Extremely",
      "qolie89_1": "In general, would you say your health is:",
      "qolie89_2": "How would you rate your overall quality of life?",
      "qolie89_3": "Compared to <b>1 year ago</b>, how would you rate your health in general <b>now</b>?",
      "qolie89_pf_head": "The following questions are about activities you might do during a typical day. Does <b>your health</b> limit you in these activities? If so, <b>how much?</b>",
      "qolie89_4": "Vigorous activities, such as running, lifting heavy objects, participating in strenuous sports",
      "qolie89_5": "Moderate activities, such as moving a table, pushing a vacuum cleaner, bowling, or playing golf",
      "qolie89_6": "Lifting or carrying groceries",
      "qolie89_7": "Climbing several flights of stairs",
      "qolie89_8": "Climbing one flight of stairs",
      "qolie89_9": "Bending, kneeling, or stooping",
      "qolie89_10": "Walking more than a mile",
      "qolie89_11": "Walking several blocks",
      "qolie89_12": "Walking one block",
      "qolie89_13": "Bathing or dressing yourself",
      "qolie89_rp_inst": "The following questions are about your regular daily activities, such as working at a job, keeping house, taking care of children, attending school, volunteer work, or taking part in community services.",
      "qolie89_rp_head": "During the <b>past 4 weeks</b>, have you had any of the following difficulties with your regular daily activities or work <b>as a result of any physical problems</b>?",
      "qolie89_14": "Cut down on the amount of time you spent on work or other activities",
      "qolie89_15": "Accomplished less than you would like",
      "qolie89_16": "Were limited in the <i>kind</i> of work or other activities you do",
      "qolie89_17": "Had <i>difficulty</i> performing the work or other activities you do (for example, it took extra effort)",
      "qolie89_rp5": "Did work or other activities <i>less carefully</i> than usual",
      "qolie89_re_head": "During the <b>past 4 weeks</b>, have you had any of the following problems with your work or other regular daily activities <b>as a result of any emotional problems</b> (such as feeling depressed or anxious)?",
      "qolie89_18": "Cut down on the amount of time you spent on work or other activities",
      "qolie89_19": "Accomplished less than you would like",
      "qolie89_20": "Didn't do work or other activities as carefully as usual",
      "qolie89_21": "How much bodily pain have you had during the past 4 weeks?",
      "qolie89_22": "During the <b>past 4 weeks</b>, how much did <b>bodily pain</b> interfere with your normal work (including both work outside the home and housework)?",
      "qolie89_ewb_head": "These questions are about how you feel and how things have been with you during the past 4 weeks.",
      "qolie89_23": "Have you been a very nervous person?",
      "qolie89_24": "Have you felt calm and peaceful?",
      "qolie89_25": "Have you felt downhearted and blue?",
      "qolie89_26": "Have you been a happy person?",
      "qolie89_27": "Have you felt so down in the dumps that nothing could cheer you up?",
      "qolie89_28": "Did you feel full of pep?",
      "qolie89_29": "Did you have a lot of energy?",
      "qolie89_30": "Did you feel worn out?",
      "qolie89_31": "Did you feel tired?",
      "qolie89_32": "In general, would you say your health is:",
      "qolie89_33": "I seem to get sick a little easier than other people.",
      "qolie89_34": "I am as healthy as anybody I know.",
      "qolie89_35": "I expect my health to get worse.",
      "qolie89_36": "My health is excellent.",
      "qolie89_37": "During the <b>past 4 weeks</b>, to what extent have your physical health or emotional problems interfered with your normal social activities with family, friends, neighbors, or groups?",
      "qolie89_38": "How often during the past 4 weeks did you socialize with friends or family?",
      "qolie89_39": "Limitations in work or volunteer activities because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_40": "Limitations in social activities because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_41": "Limitations in sexual interest or activity because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_42": "Limitations in leisure time activities because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_43": "Limitations in doing your work carefully because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_44": "Limitations in driving a car because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_45": "Limitations in recreational activities because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_46": "How satisfied are you with your social life?",
      "qolie89_47": "How satisfied are you with your family life?",
      "qolie89_cog_head": "The following questions are about problems you may have had with your memory and concentration during the past 4 weeks.",
      "qolie89_48": "How often did you have trouble with your memory?",
      "qolie89_49": "How often did you have difficulty concentrating?",
      "qolie89_50": "How often did you think slowly?",
      "qolie89_51": "How often did you have trouble with your alertness or staying awake?",
      "qolie89_52": "How often did you have trouble keeping your attention on what you were doing?",
      "qolie89_53": "How often did you have a hard time finding new information?",
      "qolie89_54": "How often did you have trouble learning new things?",
      "qolie89_55": "How often did you have trouble with tasks that require thinking?",
      "qolie89_56": "How often did you have to re-read something to understand it?",
      "qolie89_57": "How often did others have to repeat things to you?",
      "qolie89_58": "How often did you have trouble remembering recent events?",
      "qolie89_att_head": "The following questions are about your attention and concentration during the past 4 weeks.",
      "qolie89_59": "How often did you have trouble staying focused on what you were doing?",
      "qolie89_60": "How often were you easily distracted?",
      "qolie89_61": "How often did you have trouble following conversations?",
      "qolie89_62": "How often did you lose track of what you were doing?",
      "qolie89_63": "How often did you make careless mistakes?",
      "qolie89_64": "How often did you have to use extra effort to pay attention?",
      "qolie89_lang_head": "The following questions are about <b>LANGUAGE</b> problems you may have. Indicate <b>how often</b> in the <b>past 4 weeks</b> you have had these problems or how often they have interfered with your normal work or living.",
      "qolie89_65": "How often did you have trouble finding the right words when speaking?",
      "qolie89_66": "How often did you have trouble understanding what others said?",
      "qolie89_67": "How often did you have trouble reading and understanding?",
      "qolie89_68": "How often did you have difficulty expressing yourself in writing?",
      "qolie89_69": "How often did you have difficulty communicating with others?",
      "qolie89_sw_head": "The following questions are about your worries and fears about having a seizure.",
      "qolie89_70": "Having a seizure while alone",
      "qolie89_71": "Having a seizure while driving",
      "qolie89_72": "Having a seizure in front of others",
      "qolie89_73": "Being hurt or injured during a seizure",
      "qolie89_74": "Being embarrassed by a seizure",
      "qolie89_75": "Having more seizures in the future",
      "qolie89_76": "Having a seizure at work or school",
      "qolie89_med_head": "The following questions are about the effects of your epilepsy medications.",
      "qolie89_77": "How much are you bothered by the side effects of your epilepsy medication(s)?",
      "qolie89_78": "How much do side effects of your epilepsy medication(s) limit you in your daily life?",
      "qolie89_79": "How much do you worry about the long-term effects of your epilepsy medication(s)?",
      "qolie89_80": "How much do your epilepsy medications interfere with your ability to think clearly?",
      "qolie89_81": "How much do your epilepsy medications interfere with your daily activities?",
      "qolie89_hd_head": "The following questions are about how you feel about your health.",
      "qolie89_82": "How often do you feel discouraged by your health problems?",
      "qolie89_83": "How often do you feel hopeless about your health?",
      "qolie89_84": "How often do you give up trying to improve your health?",
      "qolie89_wds_head": "The following questions are about how epilepsy has affected your work, driving, and social life.",
      "qolie89_85": "Limitations in paid work because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_86": "Limitations in driving because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_87": "Limitations in social activities because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_88": "Limitations in household activities because of epilepsy",
      "qolie89_89": "How much of the time do you have access to support from people close to you?",
      "debrief": "Thank you for completing this questionnaire.",
      "qolie89_ht1": "Much better now than 1 year ago",
      "qolie89_ht2": "Somewhat better now than 1 year ago",
      "qolie89_ht3": "About the same as 1 year ago",
      "qolie89_ht4": "Somewhat worse now than 1 year ago",
      "qolie89_ht5": "Much worse now than 1 year ago",
      "qolie89_qol0": "Worst possible quality of life (as bad or worse than being dead)",
      "qolie89_qol10": "Best possible quality of life",
      "qolie89_mhvt_head": "These questions are about how you <b>FEEL</b> and how things have been for you during the <b>past 4 weeks</b>. For each question, please indicate the one answer that comes closest to the way you have been feeling.<br>How much of the time during the <b>past 4 weeks</b>...",
      "qolie89_hp_head": "Please choose the answer that best describes how <b>TRUE or FALSE</b> each of the following statements is for you.",
      "qolie89_re4": "Did work or other activities less carefully than usual",
      "qolie89_q36_head": "How much of the time during the <b>past 4 weeks</b>...",
      "qolie89_q36": "Has your epilepsy limited your social activities (such as visiting with friends or close relatives)?",
      "qolie89_q37": "Have you had difficulty concentrating and thinking?",
      "qolie89_q38": "Did you have trouble keeping your attention on an activity for long?",
      "qolie89_q39": "Were you discouraged by problems related to your health?",
      "qolie89_q40": "Have you worried about having another seizure?",
      "qolie89_q41": "Did you have difficulty reasoning and solving problems (such as making plans, making decisions, learning new things)?",
      "qolie89_q42": "Were you discouraged by your epilepsy-related problems?",
      "qolie89_q43": "Have your physical health or emotional problems interfered with your social activities (like visiting with friends, relatives, etc.)?",
      "qolie89_q48": "When there is an illness going around, I usually catch it.",
      "qolie89_q49": "How has the <b>QUALITY OF YOUR LIFE</b> been during the <b>past 4 weeks</b> (that is, how have things been going for you)?",
      "qolie89_qol_1": "Very well: could hardly be better",
      "qolie89_qol_2": "Pretty good",
      "qolie89_qol_3": "Good &amp; bad parts about equal",
      "qolie89_qol_4": "Pretty bad",
      "qolie89_qol_5": "Very bad: could hardly be worse",
      "qolie89_mem4_1": "Yes, a great deal",
      "qolie89_mem4_2": "Yes, somewhat",
      "qolie89_mem4_3": "Only a little",
      "qolie89_mem4_4": "No, not at all",
      "qolie89_mem_head": "Circle one number for <b>how often</b> in the <b>past 4 weeks</b> you have had trouble <i>remembering</i> or how often these memory problems have interfered with your normal work or living.",
      "qolie89_q51": "Names of people",
      "qolie89_q52": "Where you put things",
      "qolie89_q53": "Things people tell you",
      "qolie89_q54": "Things you read hours or days before",
      "qolie89_q55": "Finding the correct word",
      "qolie89_q56": "Understanding what others are saying in conversation",
      "qolie89_q57": "Understanding directions",
      "qolie89_q58": "Understanding what you read",
      "qolie89_q59": "Writing",
      "qolie89_conc_head": "The following questions are about <b>CONCENTRATION</b> problems you may have. Indicate <b>how often</b> in the <b>past 4 weeks</b> you had trouble concentrating or how often these problems interfered with your normal work or living.",
      "qolie89_q60": "Concentrating on conversations",
      "qolie89_q61": "Concentrating on a task or job",
      "qolie89_q62": "Concentrating on reading",
      "qolie89_q63": "Concentrating on doing one thing at a time",
      "qolie89_q64": "How often do you feel you react slowly to things that are said or done?",
      "qolie89_act_head": "The following questions are about problems you may have with certain <b>ACTIVITIES</b>. Indicate for <b>how much</b> during the <b>past 4 weeks</b> your epilepsy or antiepileptic medication has caused trouble with...",
