      "qolie89_iso_ne": "Never",
      "qolie89_vas_head": "On the scale below, please indicate how good or bad your <b>overall health</b> is today.",
      "qolie89_vas_lo": "Worst imaginable Health (as bad as or worse than being dead)",
      "qolie89_vas_hi": "Best imaginable Health",
      "qolie89_q50": "In the past 4 weeks, have you had any trouble with your memory?",
