      "qolie89_q70": "How much do you worry about hurting or injuring yourself during a seizure?",
      "qolie89_q71": "How worried are you about being embarrassed or having social problems as a result of having a seizure in the next month?",
      "qolie89_q72": "How worried are you that your epilepsy medications may be bad for you in the long run?",
      "qolie89_q73": "How well do you do with tasks involving complicated projects requiring organization or planning?",
      "qolie89_q84": "How satisfied were you with your sexual relations during the <b>past 4 weeks</b>?",
      "qolie89_q85": "How limited are your social activities compared with others your age because of your epilepsy or epilepsy-related problems?",
      "qolie89_q86": "During the <b>past 4 weeks</b>, was someone available to help you if you needed and wanted help?",
      "qolie89_q87": "How much of the time during the <b>past 4 weeks</b> did you feel left out?",
      "qolie89_q88": "During the <b>past 4 weeks</b>, how often did you feel isolated from others?",
      "qolie89_q89": "How good or bad do you think your health is? On the thermometer scale below, the best imaginable state of health is 100 and the worst imaginable state is 0. Please indicate how you feel about your health. <b>Please consider your epilepsy as part of your health when you answer this question</b>.",
